top" charoff="50"><xref ref-type="bibr" rid="bib108">108</xref>,<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="bib109">109</xref>,<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="bib110">110</xref></td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="top" charoff="50">&#x000a0;</td><td align="center" valign="top" charoff="50">Growth advantage during stationary phase growth</td><td align="center" valign="top" charoff="50"><xref ref-type="bibr" rid="bib75">75</xref></td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="top" charoff="50">&#x000a0;</td><td align="center" valign="top" charoff="50">Significant epistatic interactions between antibiotic resistance-associated mutations in <italic>rpoB</italic>, <italic>rpsL</italic> and <italic>gyrA</italic></td><td align="center" valign="top" charoff="50"><xref ref-type="bibr" rid="bib84">84</xref></td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="top" charoff="50">&#x000a0;</td><td align="center" valign="top" charoff="50">Evolution of RIF<sup>R</sup>
